 Glasgow Caledonian University is offering Nigerians with Senior Secondary School Certificates
the opportunity to apply for direct entry to the first Year of University study with a minimum of
5Bs or equivalent in their WASSCE ahead of the September 2020 Start. Applicants that meet this requirement will also not be required to present any further Certificate
for Proof of English Proficiency The University also offers 8 Installment Tuition fees payment plan to make funding easier on the
path of the parents Further information and application to the university can be made via the In-Country Representative Ikemesit
Nkereuwem-Tim via 08185594567 and Ikemesit.Nkereuwem-Tim@gcu.ac.uk or www.gcu.ac.uk/
